                - paragraph [ref=e433]:
                  - emphasis [ref=e434]:
                    - strong [ref=e435]: “
                    - text: I once worked with a woman who’d been discharged from the hospital to an Airbnb with no family to help her. The property owner called me, worried, and he didn’t feel right just leaving her there alone as she was dioriented. Together, we quickly found a senior living community that could offer the support she needed.
                - paragraph [ref=e436]
                - paragraph [ref=e437]:
                  - emphasis [ref=e438]:
                    - text: The community partner picked her up, had her assessed by a nurse, and moved her into a fully furnished apartment the very same day. I was incredibly grateful that the Airbnb owner trusted his instincts and reached out. His compassion, and our teamwork, truly changed her outcome.
